Let me start off with agreement before I flame your ass! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Yes, I agree that time is conceptual and evolved in our thinking probably due to how we percieve motion.<br>
