<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> &quot;YES, I have free will to flog my nob at this moment in 'time'. NO I do not have the free will to fly over a building, because I don't believe that I can. DO I believe I can fly? Well, yes I do. When the time becomes necassary I will fly.<br>
