ov is dead, he's just an example)  Anyway,  everyone is special, but certain ocassions call for certain tools.  Of course that is easier said than done with the ass-fucked world we live in. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showMessageRange?topicID=246.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showMessageRange?topicID=246.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showMessageRange?topicID=246.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showMessageRange?topicID=246.topic&start=81&stop=96>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showMessage?topicID=270.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showMessage?topicID=261.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=246.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.emailToFriend?topicID=246.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.threadControl?topicID=246.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=246.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=246.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="